supply <- bezier(x = c(1, 8, 9), y = c(1, 5, 9)) %>% as.data.frame()
demand <- bezier(x = c(1, 3, 9), y = c(9, 3, 1)) %>% as.data.frame()

curve_N_ponts(supply, demand, title = "Supply & Demand",linecol = c("blue", "red"))

curve_intersect(supply, demand2, gg)
